=head1 DESCRIPTION

A read-only field that represents the state of an
C<AppInstanceUserEndpoint>. Supported values:

=over

=item *

C<ACTIVE>: The C<AppInstanceUserEndpoint> is active and able to receive
messages. When C<ACTIVE>, the C<EndpointStatusReason> remains empty.

=item *

C<INACTIVE>: The C<AppInstanceUserEndpoint> is inactive and can't
receive message. When INACTIVE, the corresponding reason will be
conveyed through EndpointStatusReason.

=item *

C<INVALID_DEVICE_TOKEN> indicates that an C<AppInstanceUserEndpoint> is
C<INACTIVE> due to invalid device token

=item *

C<INVALID_PINPOINT_ARN> indicates that an C<AppInstanceUserEndpoint> is
C<INACTIVE> due to an invalid pinpoint ARN that was input through the
C<ResourceArn> field.

=back


=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Status => Str

Enum that indicates the Status of an C<AppInstanceUserEndpoint>.


=head2 StatusReason => Str

The reason for the C<EndpointStatus>.



